lead_paragraph: Marie Gulich had career highs of 27 points and 13 rebounds to help No. 22 Oregon State beat Washington State 80-58 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Gulich, No. 22 Oregon St. Women Past Washington State, 80-58
